# Widgets Directory

This directory contains reusable UI components and custom widgets.

## Suggested Structure

- `custom_button.dart` - Reusable button components
- `custom_text_field.dart` - Styled input fields
- `loading_widget.dart` - Loading indicators
- `error_widget.dart` - Error display components
- `loan_card.dart` - Loan information cards
- `transaction_tile.dart` - Transaction list items
- `language_selector.dart` - Language switching widget
